Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gigantic salamander emerges from the shadows, hungry for flesh.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Aisha tries to climb on the salamander’s back and wrestle it into a choke hold.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Aisha chokes the salamander into unconsciousness. She is unharmed in the encounter.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The salamander’s giant maw bites Aisha’s arm. She takes damage, but the salamander cowers into its den.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The floor between the entrance and exit of this chamber is segmented by large tiles with magical symbols. The tiles rest over a sticky tar-like substance.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Aisha attempts to rely on her intellect to solve the puzzle of the magical symbols.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Aisha correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. She is showered by applause from the crowd.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Aisha repeatedly steps on incorrect tiles but manages to make it across. She loses some valuables from his pack to the tar-like substance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>An ogre emerges from a lift in the center of the room
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn leaps at the ogre, trying to land a killing blow.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn stabs the ogre in the chest, killing it instantly. He is met by roaring applause from the audience watching from above.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn stabs the ogre in the chest but fails to kill it instantly. He is bashed by the ogre’s fist dealing damage before it bleeds to death.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gigantic salamander emerges from the shadows, hungry for flesh.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Aisha tries to climb on the salamander’s back and wrestle it into a choke hold.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Aisha chokes the salamander into unconsciousness. She is unharmed in the encounter.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The salamander’s giant maw bites Aisha’s arm. She takes damage, but the salamander cowers into its den.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The floor between the entrance and exit of this chamber is segmented by large tiles with magical symbols. The tiles rest over a sticky tar-like substance.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Aisha attempts to rely on her intellect to solve the puzzle of the magical symbols.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Aisha correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. She is showered by applause from the crowd.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Aisha repeatedly steps on incorrect tiles but manages to make it across. She loses some valuables from his pack to the tar-like substance.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Aisha attempts to rely on her intellect to solve the puzzle of the magical symbols.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Aisha correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. She is showered by applause from the crowd.

The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Deshawn lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Deshawn’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Deshawn’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Aisha relies on her intellect to try to solve the puzzle.
